tbbmalloc current version:

 2018 U1 released

Description:

Intel TBBMalloc interfaces for Delphi and Delphi XE versions and FreePascal with the windows 32 bit and 64 bit Dynamic Link Libraries, it is a scalable memory manager,

And how to install it ?

Just place cmem as the very first unit under the "uses" clause of your project's .dpr file.